<p><span style="color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);">早上7点20分，同学们准时到达操场集合，在各班体委的组织下整齐列队等待着晨跑的开始。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);">晨跑开始，同学们在明媚的日子里享受着微风拂过脸颊，感受着血液逐渐沸腾，用跑步开启一天的奋斗时光，用跑步展现出青春活力。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEJ1icacXhYic7ryibPE55GtgS1wVwR0NWibRiawHmotgicC3lWt9B6TEJmA5Pwq0a1CFibldjA0rQ72JrVlw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&wxfrom=13&tp=wxpic" width="317" height="236" style="width: 317px; height: 236px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);">晨跑时，同学们迈开脚步，紧跟着大部队往前冲，在红白相间的跑道上留下了整齐的脚步声，他们的步伐轻快又有力量，他们不惧疲惫，他们神采飞扬。阳光洒向运动场，尽显跑者的身影，今天的快乐，是多巴胺的释放。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEJ1icacXhYic7ryibPE55GtgS18PbYhWzNSDMDDp8OblOvqp5FricY9FCSIuFYKhuCHr9Lxv7c3BcJ7tg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="340" height="229" style="width: 340px; height: 229px;"/></span></span></p>